Philip McKeon https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Philip_McKeon 0 Philip Anthony McKeon (born November 11, 1964) is an American actor. He is known for playing the role of Tommy Hyatt, the son of the title character, on the sitcom Alice, from 1976 to 1985. Philip_Anthony_McKeon ( born November_11_,_1964 ) is an_American_actor .
